{"id": 2000, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi de M. Olivier Falorni relative \u00e0 la fin de vie (1100)., n\u00b0\u00a01364-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1364/AN/2000", "date": "2025-05-09", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Vincent", "last_name": "Tr\u00e9buchet", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "Bartolom\u00e9", "last_name": "Lenoir", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9ric", "last_name": "Michoux", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "Olivier", "last_name": "Fayssat", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "G\u00e9rault", "last_name": "Verny", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "Christophe", "last_name": "Bentz", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Eddy", "last_name": "Casterman", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Marie-France", "last_name": "Lorho", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Mich\u00e8le", "last_name": "Martinez", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "K\u00e9vin", "last_name": "Mauvieux", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Pierre", "last_name": "Meurin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thibaut", "last_name": "Monnier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Odoul", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Rambaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sophie-Laurence", "last_name": "Roy", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Sicard", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Limongi", "party": "Rassemblement National"}], "summary": "Faire passer l'aide \u00e0 mourir pour un droit\u00a0risquerait de transformer une d\u00e9rogation tr\u00e8s encadr\u00e9e en une pr\u00e9tendue \u00ab\u202fpr\u00e9rogative\u202f\u00bb, incompatible avec la philosophie m\u00eame du soin et de la protection.\nQualifier l\u2019aide \u00e0 mourir de droit ouvrirait en outre la voie \u00e0 des revendications d\u2019\u00ab\u202fautomatisation\u202f\u00bb ou de \u00ab\u202ffacilitation\u202f\u00bb, alors que le l\u00e9gislateur a choisi un r\u00e9gime fond\u00e9 sur des conditions sine qua non : pathologie incurable, volont\u00e9 libre et r\u00e9it\u00e9r\u00e9e, avis\u00a0externes etc.\nIl convient ainsi de revenir \u00e0 la r\u00e9daction initiale de cet article 2."}